{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2015}} {{Infobox film awards | number = 1 | award = [[Nollywood Movies Awards]] | image = | caption = | date = 2 June 2012 | site = | host = Julius Agwu, [[Kate Henshaw]] | producer = | director = | organizer = [[Nollywood Movies|Nollywood Movies Network]] | best_picture = [[Tango with Me]] | most_wins = | most_nominations = | last = | next = [[2013 Nollywood Movies Awards|2nd]] }}
The maiden edition of the [[Nollywood Movies Awards]] was held at the Civic Center in Lagos Nigeria on 2 June 2012 to reward excellence of film professionals in [[Nollywood]]. ''[[Tango with Me]]'' and ''[[Mirror Boy]]'' won the most awards. [[Genevieve Nnaji]] and [[Ramsey Nouah]] won the viewer's choice awards for the female and male categories respectively by popular vote.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.africanspotlight.com/2012/06/06/video-nollywood-movies-awards-2012-stars-sparkle-on-red-carpet/ | title=NMA 2012 Red carpet | accessdate=21 March 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://dailypost.ng/2012/06/06/nollywood-movies-award-2012-sparkle-on-red-carpet-courtesy-iroktv/ | title=NMA 2012 | accessdate=21 March 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nollywoodmoviesawards.tv/nma-nominees/ | title=NMA Winners | accessdate=21 March 2014}}</ref>
